{
  "name": "Locus: Weapon +1",
  "type": "equipment",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"item-attunement\"><p><em>(Requires attunement by a creature. The properties of this item are affixed to a weapon.)</em></p></div><p><em>This item is a @UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.rules.JournalEntry.nniVtdJB1oyk5Sa3]{locus} and can be combined with other <strong>Loci </strong>per the @UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.rules.JournalEntry.nniVtdJB1oyk5Sa3.JournalEntryPage.zI0VWGKnYZqz6sKd]{Combining Loci} rules.</em></p><p>This Locus merges magically merges with a <strong>weapon</strong> of your choice. This can be done during a short or long rest, requires 10 minutes to complete.  Upon completion, the quality of the weapon visibly improves. Once completed, the item becomes magical.</p><p><strong>Effect:</strong> While affixed, the weapon gains a +1 bonus to attack and damage rolls made with the weapon.</p><p><strong>Note:</strong> This can be applied to hand wraps, brass knuckles and other similar items that would represent Unarmed Strikes.  The Unarmed Strikes would the be considered the weapon and these Unarmed Strikes would be what benefits from the item.</p>",
